<div> </div>
<div class="g12">
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><u>For The Third Consecutive Year, Inghams Wins Best Operator For Activities <br />At The Travel Weekly Globe Travel Awards 2018</u></strong></p>
<p>For the third year in a row, Inghams is the proud winner of the accolade for <strong>Best Operator for</strong> <strong>Activities</strong> at the Travel Weekly Globe Travel Awards 2018. The award was collected by Simon McIntyre, Head of Sales, at the lavish awards ceremony held in Grosvenor House, London, on 11<sup>th</sup> January 2018.</p>
<p>At the black-tie event, Paul Carter, Chief Operating Officer, said, "We’re over the moon to have been awarded this prestigious trophy for the third consecutive time and it’s an honour for Inghams to again be recognised at one of the most important events in the travel industry calendar. We thank all our travel agent partners for voting for us, without whom we could not be where we are today, and we thank our passionate staff for always putting our guests first and for constantly ensuring the Inghams name remains synonymous with success!”</p>
<p>The Travel Weekly Globe Travel Awards <em>recognise the hard work, dedication and commitment of the very best companies and individuals of the travel trade, as voted for by UK Travel Agents. </em></p>
<p>The Golden Globe Trophy will be on display at Inghams HQ from today, alongside the Trophies from 2016 and 2017.</p>
<p><strong>For more information, visit </strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk"><strong>www.inghams.co.uk</strong></a><strong>, call 01483 791 114 or follow @InghamsSki and @InghamsSummer.  </strong></p>
<p><strong>-ENDS-</strong></p>
